creator: Namanbir Singh
descriptionHtml:
We're always concerned about our loved ones.

Everyone should be!

Even I am concerned for my sisters and grandparents when they go out.

The news about incidents like Rape and Kidnapping increases my concern.

I believe that one day this will change, the world will be a safe place. But we can't till that happens.

So, a small step towards safety from my side.
A glimpse of the Future.

I proudly present you SHIELD.

SHIELD acts as a Shield 🛡 for your loved ones.

Sensing any danger? Turn protection ON, keep the app RUNNING in the background and it will keep listening for distress calls.

You just need to say 'Help', and SHIELD will inform your parents/guardians that you're in danger via SMS.
Not only this, but SHIELD will also share your live location with them.

SHIELD will protect anyone, whether it's women or men or children or elders.

Please note that the app needs to have access to your location while in background to make sure the SOS feature works correctly in the time of need. You may ignore any notifications android may give you towards Shield using location in background.

Reach me out at namanbir@programmingbuddy.io
descriptionShort: Just say, Help and your loved ones will be shared your live location via SMS

Yours truly,

title: SHIELD - Protecting women

creator: Namanbir Singh
descriptionHtml:
The world has good people and bad people too!

We are always worried when any of our family members go out.
What if someone tries to harm them? What if someone does anything wrong with my sister? What if someone kidnaps my grandfather?

I believe that one day this will change, and the world will be a safe place.
But we can't wait till that happens.

So, a small initiative towards the safety of your loved ones.
SHIELD acts as a Shield 🛡 for your loved ones.

Going out alone? Turn Protection ON, and it will trigger the SOS when you scream 'Help'

SHIELD will inform your parents that you're in danger via SMS.
Not just this, SHIELD will also share your location with them.

Made in India, Made for the World! 🇮🇳
descriptionShort: Just scream 'Help' and your loved ones will be informed that you're in danger

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We have redesigned the entire application to ensure that everything is really easy for you. Everything is simplified to make the process very smooth.

If you face any kind of issue with this new version, feel free to contact us at namanbir@shieldindia.org anytime.

Together, we'll make this world a better and safer place!

We are excited to announce that this is the biggest update to the SHIELD app.

We have added a New "Swipe to send SOS" feature, using this you can send an SOS to your Emergency contacts easily in less than a second.

Apart from this, there are multiple minor improvements and we have also fixed some known bugs.

You can share your feedback at namanbir@shieldindia.org
